Module com.example.protrack

Class ExpandedEmployeeController

java.lang.Object
com.example.protrack.applicationpages.ExpandedEmployeeController
public class ExpandedEmployeeController extends Object
Controller for the expanded view of an employee's details. This class manages the display of an employee's information and statistics, as well as handling navigation and employee removal functionality.
